{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.1","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 7:1","prev_osis_id":"Heb.006.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.007.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-10: cf. Ge 14:17-20.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.7.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>En effet, ce Melchis\u00e9dek, roi de Salem, sacrificateur du Dieu Tr\u00e8s-Haut, qui alla au-devant d\u2019Abraham lorsqu\u2019il revenait de la d\u00e9faite des rois, qui le b\u00e9nit,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.7","name":"H\u00e9breux 7","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.2","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:2","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.6.20","name":"H\u00e9breux 6:20","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.6.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.2","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 7:2","prev_osis_id":"Heb.007.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.007.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.7.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>et \u00e0 qui Abraham donna la d\u00eeme de tout, qui est d\u2019abord roi de justice, d\u2019apr\u00e8s la signification de son nom, ensuite roi de Salem, c\u2019est-\u00e0-dire roi de paix,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.7","name":"H\u00e9breux 7","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.3","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:3","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.1","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:1","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.3","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 7:3","prev_osis_id":"Heb.007.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.007.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.7.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>qui est sans p\u00e8re, sans m\u00e8re, sans g\u00e9n\u00e9alogie, qui n\u2019a ni commencement de jours ni fin de vie, mais qui est rendu semblable au Fils de Dieu, ce Melchis\u00e9dek demeure sacrificateur \u00e0 perp\u00e9tuit\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.7","name":"H\u00e9breux 7","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.4","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:4","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.2","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:2","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.4","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 7:4","prev_osis_id":"Heb.007.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.007.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.7.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Consid\u00e9rez combien est grand celui auquel le patriarche Abraham donna la d\u00eeme du butin.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.7","name":"H\u00e9breux 7","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.5","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:5","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.3","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:3","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.5","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 7:5","prev_osis_id":"Heb.007.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.007.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.7.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Ceux des fils de L\u00e9vi qui exercent le sacerdoce ont, d\u2019apr\u00e8s la loi, l\u2019ordre de lever la d\u00eeme sur le peuple, c\u2019est-\u00e0-dire, sur leurs fr\u00e8res, qui cependant sont issus des reins d\u2019Abraham;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.7","name":"H\u00e9breux 7","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.6","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:6","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.4","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:4","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.6","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 7:6","prev_osis_id":"Heb.007.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.007.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.7.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>et lui, qui ne tirait pas d\u2019eux son origine, il leva la d\u00eeme sur Abraham, et il b\u00e9nit celui qui avait les promesses.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.7","name":"H\u00e9breux 7","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.7","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:7","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.5","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:5","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.7","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 7:7","prev_osis_id":"Heb.007.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.007.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.7.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Or c\u2019est sans contredit l\u2019inf\u00e9rieur qui est b\u00e9ni par le sup\u00e9rieur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.7","name":"H\u00e9breux 7","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.8","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:8","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.6","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:6","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.8","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 7:8","prev_osis_id":"Heb.007.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.007.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.7.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Et ici, ceux qui per\u00e7oivent la d\u00eeme sont des hommes mortels; mais l\u00e0, c\u2019est celui dont il est attest\u00e9 qu\u2019il est vivant.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.7","name":"H\u00e9breux 7","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.9","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:9","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.7","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:7","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.9","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 7:9","prev_osis_id":"Heb.007.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.007.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.7.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>De plus, L\u00e9vi, qui per\u00e7oit la d\u00eeme, l\u2019a pay\u00e9e, pour ainsi dire, par Abraham;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.7","name":"H\u00e9breux 7","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.8","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:8","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.10","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 7:10","prev_osis_id":"Heb.007.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.007.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.7.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>car il \u00e9tait encore dans les reins de son p\u00e8re, lorsque Melchis\u00e9dek alla au-devant d\u2019Abraham.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.7","name":"H\u00e9breux 7","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.11","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:11","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.9","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:9","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.11","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 7:11","prev_osis_id":"Heb.007.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.007.012,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 11-28: cf. Ps 110:4. H\u00e9 8; 9:6-12; 10:10-14.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.7.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>\n    Si donc la perfection avait \u00e9t\u00e9 possible par le sacerdoce L\u00e9vitique, car c\u2019est sur ce sacerdoce que repose la loi donn\u00e9e au peuple, qu\u2019\u00e9tait-il encore besoin qu\u2019il par\u00fbt un autre sacrificateur selon l\u2019ordre de Melchis\u00e9dek, et non selon l\u2019ordre d\u2019Aaron?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.7","name":"H\u00e9breux 7","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.12","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:12","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.12","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 7:12","prev_osis_id":"Heb.007.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.007.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.7.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Car, le sacerdoce \u00e9tant chang\u00e9, n\u00e9cessairement aussi il y a un changement de loi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.7","name":"H\u00e9breux 7","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.13","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:13","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.11","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:11","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.13","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 7:13","prev_osis_id":"Heb.007.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.007.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.7.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>En effet, celui de qui ces choses sont dites appartient \u00e0 une autre tribu, dont aucun membre n\u2019a fait le service de l\u2019autel;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.7","name":"H\u00e9breux 7","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.14","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:14","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.12","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:12","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.14","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 7:14","prev_osis_id":"Heb.007.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.007.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.7.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>car il est notoire que notre Seigneur est sorti de Juda, tribu dont Mo\u00efse n\u2019a rien dit pour ce qui concerne le sacerdoce.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.7","name":"H\u00e9breux 7","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.15","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:15","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.13","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:13","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.15","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 7:15","prev_osis_id":"Heb.007.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.007.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.7.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Cela devient plus \u00e9vident encore, quand il para\u00eet un autre sacrificateur \u00e0 la ressemblance de Melchis\u00e9dek,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.7","name":"H\u00e9breux 7","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.16","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:16","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.14","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:14","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.16","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 7:16","prev_osis_id":"Heb.007.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.007.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.7.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>institu\u00e9, non d\u2019apr\u00e8s la loi d\u2019une ordonnance charnelle, mais selon la puissance d\u2019une vie imp\u00e9rissable;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.7","name":"H\u00e9breux 7","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.17","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:17","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.15","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:15","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.17","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 7:17","prev_osis_id":"Heb.007.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.007.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.7.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>car ce t\u00e9moignage lui est rendu:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">\n    Tu es sacrificateur pour toujours Selon l\u2019ordre de Melchis\u00e9dek.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.7","name":"H\u00e9breux 7","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.18","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:18","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.16","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:16","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.18","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 7:18","prev_osis_id":"Heb.007.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.007.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Heb.7.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Il y a ainsi abolition d\u2019une ordonnance ant\u00e9rieure, \u00e0 cause de son impuissance et de son inutilit\u00e9,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.7","name":"H\u00e9breux 7","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.19","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:19","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.17","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:17","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.19","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 7:19","prev_osis_id":"Heb.007.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.007.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Heb.7.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>car la loi n\u2019a rien amen\u00e9 \u00e0 la perfection, et introduction d\u2019une meilleure esp\u00e9rance, par laquelle nous nous approchons de Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.7","name":"H\u00e9breux 7","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.20","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:20","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.18","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:18","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.20","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 7:20","prev_osis_id":"Heb.007.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.007.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Heb.7.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Et, comme cela n\u2019a pas eu lieu sans serment,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.7","name":"H\u00e9breux 7","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.21","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:21","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.19","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:19","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.21","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 7:21","prev_osis_id":"Heb.007.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.007.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Heb.7.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>car, tandis que les L\u00e9vites sont devenus sacrificateurs sans serment, J\u00e9sus l\u2019est devenu avec serment par celui qui lui a dit:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">\n    Le Seigneur a jur\u00e9, et il ne se repentira pas:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Tu es sacrificateur pour toujours,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Selon l\u2019ordre de Melchis\u00e9dek.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.7","name":"H\u00e9breux 7","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.22","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:22","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.20","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:20","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.22","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 7:22","prev_osis_id":"Heb.007.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.007.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Heb.7.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>J\u00e9sus est par cela m\u00eame le garant d\u2019une alliance plus excellente.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.7","name":"H\u00e9breux 7","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.23","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:23","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.21","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:21","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.23","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 7:23","prev_osis_id":"Heb.007.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.007.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Heb.7.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>De plus, il y a eu des sacrificateurs en grand nombre, parce que la mort les emp\u00eachait d\u2019\u00eatre permanents.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.7","name":"H\u00e9breux 7","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.24","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:24","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.22","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:22","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.24","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 7:24","prev_osis_id":"Heb.007.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.007.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Heb.7.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Mais lui, parce qu\u2019il demeure \u00e9ternellement, poss\u00e8de un sacerdoce qui n\u2019est pas transmissible.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.7","name":"H\u00e9breux 7","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.25","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:25","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.23","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:23","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.25","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 7:25","prev_osis_id":"Heb.007.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.007.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Heb.7.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>C\u2019est aussi pour cela qu\u2019il peut sauver parfaitement ceux qui s\u2019approchent de Dieu par lui, \u00e9tant toujours vivant pour interc\u00e9der en leur faveur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.7","name":"H\u00e9breux 7","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.26","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:26","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.24","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:24","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.26","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 7:26","prev_osis_id":"Heb.007.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.007.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Heb.7.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Il nous convenait, en effet, d\u2019avoir un souverain sacrificateur comme lui, saint, innocent, sans tache, s\u00e9par\u00e9 des p\u00e9cheurs, et plus \u00e9lev\u00e9 que les cieux,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.7","name":"H\u00e9breux 7","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.27","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:27","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.25","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:25","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.27","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 7:27","prev_osis_id":"Heb.007.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.007.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Heb.7.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>qui n\u2019a pas besoin, comme les souverains sacrificateurs, d\u2019offrir chaque jour des sacrifices, d\u2019abord pour ses propres p\u00e9ch\u00e9s, ensuite pour ceux du peuple, car ceci, il l\u2019a fait une fois pour toutes en s\u2019offrant lui-m\u00eame.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.7","name":"H\u00e9breux 7","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.28","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:28","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.26","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:26","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.28","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 7:28","prev_osis_id":"Heb.007.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.008.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Heb.7.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>En effet, la loi \u00e9tablit souverains sacrificateurs des hommes sujets \u00e0 la faiblesse; mais la parole du serment qui a \u00e9t\u00e9 fait apr\u00e8s la loi \u00e9tablit le Fils, qui est parfait pour l\u2019\u00e9ternit\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.7","name":"H\u00e9breux 7","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.8.1","name":"H\u00e9breux 8:1","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.8.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.7.27","name":"H\u00e9breux 7:27","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.7.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fc9ddc7a5.44972521');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fc9ddc7a5.44972521\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fc9ddc7a5.44972521","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fc9ddc7a5.44972521'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fc9ddc7a5.44972521\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}